This application is released as an open source project for educational purposes. Uses Rails 5, React, Boostrap, Device, Simple_Form, Prawn, PaperClip and ActiveAdmin.' %></p>
                  <%= link_to t("helpers.links.sign_up"), new_user_registration_path , :class=>"btn-ui-ux btn btn-danger btn-lg mb-5" %>
				  <div id="github-img-div">
				  	<%= link_to image_tag("github.png"), "https://github.com/papayalabs/pymenta", :class=>"btn-ui-ux" %>
				  </div>
			  	  
            </div>
        
    </section>

